import Vue from 'vue'
import VueProgressBar from 'vue-progressbar'
import Pagination from '@/components/pagination'
Vue.use(VueProgressBar, {
    color: '#7009FF',
    failedColor: '#1a11e8',
    thickness: '2px',
    transition: {
        speed: '0.3s',
        opacity: '0.6s',
        termination: 300
    },
    autoRevert: true,
    location: 'top',
    inverse: false
})
Vue.component('pagination', Pagination)
